description.narrative: This activity (CHASE Operations Team deployments) is a component of UK response to Ebola Crisis through support for the Joint Inter Agency Task Force (JIATF) reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Humanitarian assistance' and a budget of £4,557,660. This component benefits Sierra Leone, and works in the following sector(s): Relief co-ordination and support services. , with the following implementing partners: Crown Agents Limited. The start date is 29-10-2014 and the end date is 31-03-2016.
